   /*
    * Relational operator         Can be written
    * IS GREATER THAN             IS >
    * IS NOT GREATER THAN         IS NOT >
    * IS LESS THAN                IS <
    * IS NOT LESS THAN            IS NOT <
    * IS EQUAL TO                 IS =
    * IS NOT EQUAL TO             IS NOT =
    * IS GREATER THAN OR EQUAL TO IS >=
    * IS LESS THAN OR EQUAL TO    IS <=
